{"tid":589773,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關狗到依加仲想掩飾","createTime":"2018-03-12T05:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T12:39:01.000Z","uid":38523,"like":31,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4d3d141c74982a4aaebfbf8e4c14b447edb2ee","tid":589773,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"叫人投白票下話？<br />\n滿意未？<br />\n明知保皇狗鐵票<br />\n仲叫人投白票<br />\n用泛民過橋叫人投白票<br />\n結果正如我之前所講<br />\n保皇狗得益<br />\n之前佢一直扮睇唔到架<br />\n依加又點解釋？"},{"pid":"bf3a390586ce64e2b5b817afc44993c6e890f700","tid":589773,"uid":30988,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"佢擺明係想玩柒泛民<br />\n等佢地反省吓嘛？<br />\n<br />\n有掩飾咩？"},{"pid":"c441e355e69efa9cee9122e59eac16e9cb003af3","tid":589773,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"搶到第二席有bonus<br />\nfat fat la"},{"pid":"5ab1586c5399b5ac794abb37872b03f98686cee4","tid":589773,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bf3a390586ce64e2b5b817afc44993c6e890f700","tid":589773,"uid":30988,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"佢擺明係想玩柒泛民<br />\n等佢地反省吓嘛？<br />\n<br />\n有掩飾咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:39:02.000Z","msg":"扮乜野啊<br />\n借呢點暗助保皇狗就真<br />\n保皇狗唔洗反省？<br />\n起佢底睇下<br />\n有幾何屌過保皇狗？<br />\n投完票先屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055d58e10196b758377a42b4c365707dd9dc229d","tid":589773,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7d992e11b82531c73660d9a102e77d6a7a5feb","tid":589773,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T01:19:47.000Z","msg":"大家都係反毛手足<br />\n唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f